data.description: An ACREAGE!! EXTREMELY CLOSE TO TOWN!! On a HARD SURFACE ROAD!! This and much more could be YOURS in this 4 bed, 2 bath home with over 2200 sq foot of living space! Original woodwork and stained glass in a number of areas. Main floor has multiple rooms for living, dining, office as well as main floor laundry and a full bath. 2nd floor has 4 bedrooms with a 5th room for whatever suits your family's needs as well as a beautifully updated bathroom with tile walk in shower. Outside, home sits on just over an acre with 2 single detached garages, a shed and plenty of room to enjoy the outdoors with privacy!! INTERESTED?!?!?!? CALL TODAY to take a look!!
